* edit php.ini in /usr/local/php5/lib.
  add Asia/Calcutta to timezone:   
     date.timezone = Asia/Calcutta
  add socket path:
     mysql.default_socket=/tmp/mysql.sock
     mysqli.default_socket=/tmp/mysql.sock
     pdo_mysql.default_socket=/tmp/mysql.sock
  restart apache
* add write permissions to core/* directories
* admin user is modx/modx123

